,A.DV_1 DV_1 ,A.DV_2 DV_2 ,A.DV_3 DV_3 ,A.DV_4 DV_4 ,A.DV_5 DV_5 ,FN_DRG_JUNINP_YN(A.FKOCS2003) HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,A.JUSA JUSA ,D.SUNAME SUNAME ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.FKOCS2003 FKOCS2003 ,A.APPEND_YN APPEND_YN ,A.RE_USE_YN RE_USE_YN ,A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE ,A.HOPE_TIME HOPE_TIME FROM OUT0101 D, DRG0120 C, INV0110 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.HOPE_DATE = :f_hope_date AND A.HOPE_TIME = :f_hope_time AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND A.RESIDENT = :f_doctor AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN,'N') LIKE :f_magam_gubun AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('4') AND NVL(EMERGENCY,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(TOIWON_DRG_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS NULL AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND A.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND B.JAERYO_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND :f_magam_bunryu = '2' ORDER BY 1, 2, 25

data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.BUNHO BUNHO ,B.SUNAME SUNAME ,B.SEX SEX ,FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(A.ORDER_DATE, B.BIRTH, '') AGE ,A.HO_DONG HO_DONG ,A.RESIDENT RESIDENT ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.RESIDENT, A.ORDER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME ,C.HO_DONG1 HO_DONG ,NVL(A.APPEND_YN,'N') APPEND_YN ,DECODE(A.BUNRYU1,'4','Y','N') JUSA_YN ,A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE ,A.HOPE_TIME HOPE_TIME ,A.HOPE_DATE OLD_HOPE_DATE ,A.HOPE_TIME OLD_HOPE_TIME FROM INP1001 C, OUT0101 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(EMERGENCY,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(TOIWON_DRG_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS NULL AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND A.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') != 'Y' AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND C.PKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND NVL(C.CANCEL_YN,'N') = 'N' AND C.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND NVL(C.TOIWON_GOJI_YN, 'N') = 'N' ORDER BY 10, 11, 12
